title: It's Time To Stop James Charles - H3 Podcast # 241
description: On this episode of the H3 Podcast Ethan breaks down the ever growing list of children accusing James Charles of grooming them, we debate the pros and cons of Chet Hank's white boy summer, and Ethan brings himself to tears with his most brilliant idea ever!
